      • addProvider

        public static void addProvider()
        Adds a provider by prompting the user for information, which is then funneled into a parameterized ProviderData constructor. Then, stores the new ProviderData into the providerList arraylist.

      • deleteProvider

        public static void deleteProvider()
        Deletes a provider given the number of a provider which is prompted for within the method.

      • updateProvider

        public static void updateProvider()
        Prompts the user to input the number of the provider they wish to update, then the field they wish to update.

      • validateProvider

        public static boolean validateProvider()
        Validates a provider by checking a given provider number against all the existing providers which are stored within the system.
        Returns:
        true if a match exists

      • validateCode

        public static boolean validateCode​(java.lang.String providerNumber)
        Similar to the above verification function, however this method simply accepts a String as a parameter and returns whether or not it's a valid provider number without prompting the user or confirming/denying the validation through a print method.
        Parameters:
        providerNumber - a valid provider number which may or may not be validated
        Returns:
        true if providerNumber is an existent provider number

      • addService

        public static void addService​(java.lang.String providerNumber,
                              ServiceData newService)
        Adds a service to a specified provider, given a valid provider number and service.
        Parameters:
        providerNumber - The provider number which specifies which ProviderData object to store the ServiceData within.
        newService - The ServiceData which will be stored within a ProviderData object.

      • getProviderList

        public static java.util.ArrayList<ProviderData> getProviderList()
        Gets the list of all providers who are a part of the ChocAn network.
        Returns:
        ArrayList which is populated with ProviderData objects which correspond to the providers who are a part of the ChocAn network.
